name: Queer NFT; Series 3; No. 2
description: @queernft - An established artist claiming an NFT space for queer expression. The commercial world of art has held our community back, prevented us from showing work that reflects 100% of who we are. So I am here now, sharing my hidden works with the world as NFT. Series 3, a 16 painting abstraction study using snapchat submitted pics to explore a lighter side of the penis, oil on canvas.
